headline: From Fox News to NBC, Legacy Media Wants In on TikTok
summary: Big news brands were slow to join the video platform but now are experimenting with reaching a new audience there.

headline: MSNBC and CNN Fight to Dig Out of a Postelection Ratings Hole
summary: Ratings for the No. 2 and No. 3 cable news networks have plummeted since Donald Trump’s victory, while Fox News remains the leader.
